<div id="header">
  <%= image_tag "logo.png", :size => "32x32", :id => "logo", :alt => "Logo" %>
  <h1>SkateHamilton</h1>

  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>

<div id="container">
  <ul id="options">
    <li><%= link_to 'Home', root_url %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'About', about_url %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'Contact', contact_url, :class => 'active' %></li>
    <li><%= link_to 'Developers', api_url %></li>
  </ul>

  <div id="contents">
    <h1>Contact SkateHamilton</h1>
    <p>
      We can be contacted through a few different ways.  First, you can use the contact form on this page.  Second, you can join our <a href="#">Google Group</a> or tweet us with the hashtag #OpenHamilton and we'll try our best to get back to you.  If you want to tell us about a rink we missed, you can do some on the left panel of our <%= link_to 'home page', root_url %>.
    </p>

    <form action="#add" method="POST">
      <label for="email">Email address</label><br/>
      <input type="text" id="email" name="email" /><br/><br/>
      <label for="details">Comments</label><br/>
      <textarea id="details" name="details" rows="5"></textarea><br/>

      <input type="submit" name="submit" value="Submit" />
    </form>
  </div>

</div>